{"tid":652144,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"印度男睇《復仇者3》傷心過度於戲院猝死","createTime":"2018-05-03T15:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T09:53:35.000Z","uid":153341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3b21bc26e49e826c6731ec0f59a440bd2d93016a","tid":652144,"uid":153341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T15:32:49.000Z","msg":"Marvel巨作《復仇者聯盟3 : 無限之戰》(Avengers : Infinity War)，睇完後確實令人幾傷感，因為有主要角色被「消失」，令不少「復仇者迷」非常傷心，近日喺美國已傳出幾單觀眾睇完《復仇者3》後不適送院嘅新聞。日前，印度一名男子睇《復仇者3》期間猝死<br />\n<br />\n印度傳媒報道，喺5月1日「勞動節」當日，一名43歲嘅建築工人Peddapasupula Baasha喺Proddatur嘅Cinehub Multiplex戲院睇3D版《復仇者3》，當電影完結，彩蛋亦播完後，佢依然坐喺座位上，工作人員走埋佢身邊叫佢，佢仍然唔郁。工作人員就幫佢除下3D眼鏡，就發覺佢已經死亡，而且仲睜開眼睛。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，呢位男觀眾可能係過度緊張導致心臟病發死亡。亦有網民指，因為《復仇者3》太多英雄消失，令呢位男觀眾太過傷心，所以離世了。"},{"pid":"877d051b86e7ffab0ec0739496b4c0a780c2e033","tid":652144,"uid":153341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T15:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"657277556c422c5f3ac1586bf43d5b99fa692ae1","tid":652144,"uid":182930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T16:08:58.000Z","msg":"Thanos撻一達手指就無咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa6b1ee6ab6d5de73040114ccfc3ddb10892aa2","tid":652144,"uid":838,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T16:29:18.000Z","msg":"撻一撻手指，連觀眾都死埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e462ac77f30dd11a18d5287cd8accf84e8f73f","tid":652144,"uid":71441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T09:46:25.000Z","msg":"食得太多偉哥"},{"pid":"a68a8a20af5bf53ca3bc06b3cba7f8b9f5b8de54","tid":652144,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T09:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}